posts.post_content:
Hello - I am down to 44 cards needed to finish my T206 set. I am looking to purchase the following cards in Fair to VGEX condition, graded or raw. I don't mind Poor cards as long as the front presents decent. Please email me at [url]bucklercards@yahoo.com[/url] with any for sale. I will also trade for cards I need. Thank you for everyones help so far. 

Thanks, Chris
